  },
  {
    name: 'Donna Davi',
    role: 'Verified Client',
    quote: 'I had several real estate questions which gave me a lot of anxiety. I saw one of Cody Posey videos which I found to be very informative, easy to understand. I reached out to him. Cody responded immediately. He was selfless with his time, which I appreciated. He answered my questions, he was patient. I highly recommend him. Thank you Cody!!',
    initials: 'DD',
    date: '30 weeks ago',
  },
  {
    name: 'Mara',
    role: 'Google Local Guide',
    quote: "We had the best experience with Cody! He took his time, even spontaneously on the same day to help us finding our home. Everything went smoothly and he took care of the whole process and still after everything was signed and we moved in he's still there to help us with any questions. We can highly recommend him. Thank you!",
    initials: 'M',
    date: '35 weeks ago',
  },
  {
    name: 'Shannon Cheatham',
    role: 'Google Local Guide',
    quote: 'Cody was a pleasure to work with. He went above and beyond and exemplifies true customer service! We would highly recommend him if you are selling or buying a home! He helped in many different ways to ensure EVERYTHING was perfect. Thank you Cody for going above and beyond expectations!',
    initials: 'SC',
    date: '35 weeks ago',
  },
