    initials: 'MD',
    date: '46 weeks ago',
  },
  {
    name: "Shasta's Glow",
    role: 'Home Buyer',
    quote: 'God truly blessed us when he sent Cody Posey our way when we were looking for our new home. He truly pays attention to what you want, need, and everything in between. He offered great insight so that we could make the best decision financially for our family. He worked with us from out of state and called and texted often to keep us updated on everything. He is your guy trust me.',
    initials: 'SG',
    date: '48 weeks ago',
  },
  {
    name: 'Greg Van Leer',
    role: 'Home Buyer',
    quote: "Cody has always been a pleasure to work with. He has an outstanding knowledge of the home buying process. He also will go above and beyond for anyone who works with him. He will not only inspect the home thoroughly but he will tell you what's needed and not needed before purchase. He is also one of the most honest and hardest working persons I've ever met. I look forward to working with him on multiple properties to come!",
    initials: 'GV',
    date: '50 weeks ago',
  },
  {
    name: 'Aaron H',
    role: 'Google Local Guide',
    quote: "On the ball! Cody helped me sort out a property tax issue and uncovered that my mortgage company was overcharging me for the past few years. In just a few hours he was able to get past the road blocks that I encountered and even was responsive well into the evening hours as to what steps I needed to take. Because of his help, we were able to enroll our child into a better after school program which we will reap the benefits of for years to come! Cody is my first call for any and everything home related!",
    initials: 'AH',
    date: 'Mar 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Anna Chandler',
    role: 'Verified Client',
    quote: 'Super great to work with.',
    initials: 'AC',
    date: 'Mar 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Ferrol Bell',
    role: 'New Construction Buyer',
    quote: "Cody was phenomenal from start to finish. Our home buying process went extremely fast and felt like a whirlwind but Cody handled it all knowing how hectic our schedules. He even caught that the builders gutter crew installed the gutters improperly. He's more than willing to go above and beyond for any of his clients and once it's all said and done I'm sure you'll feel like you gained a new family member. Thanks again, Cody — The Bell Family",
    initials: 'FB',
    date: 'Mar 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Cesar Bartolo',
    role: 'Home Buyer',
    quote: "I had the pleasure of working with Cody during the process, and I couldn't have asked for a better experience. From the very beginning, Cody was incredibly professional, knowledgeable, and attentive to my needs. He took the time to understand what I was looking for in a home and provided excellent guidance throughout every step of the journey. What really stood out was Cody's commitment to making sure I felt comfortable and informed. He was always available to answer questions, provided great advice, and helped me navigate any challenges that came up. I highly recommend Cody to anyone looking for a trustworthy, reliable, and dedicated realtor. He goes above and beyond to ensure his clients have a smooth and successful experience. I'm grateful for all his hard work and would definitely work with him again in the future!",
    initials: 'CB',
    date: 'Mar 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Daisy Lopez',
    role: 'Relocation Buyer',
    quote: 'Hands down the most AMAZING realtor to work with. Coming from California to Texas was the best decision we made, especially with Cody on our side. His work ethics is highly visible. His hospitality and knowledge were incredible. We spent a weekend looking at homes all over San Antonio and fell in love with our dream home in Garden Ridge. Not one question we had did Cody leave unanswered. I will say Cody has gone above and beyond not only as our Realtor but now a friend.',
    initials: 'DL',
    date: 'Mar 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Joe Espinoza',
    role: 'Home Seller',
    quote: 'We enjoyed working with Cody. We appreciated his guidance, patience during the process of the sale. He is very professional and detailed my family and I recommend him highly. Thank you Cody. — Gloria DeLaCerdaEspinoza & Family',
    initials: 'JE',
    date: 'Feb 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Chance Alwin',
    role: 'Verified Client',
    quote: "Cody's professionalism and expertise made this transaction seamless. He brings a high level of communication and energy and is always willing to go the extra mile to serve his clients at the highest level. I would highly recommend utilizing Cody for your future real estate needs.",
    initials: 'CA',
    date: 'Feb 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Eric McNamara',
    role: 'Home Buyer & Seller',
    quote: "Cody is an awesome realtor. We wanted to work with him after he did an amazing job with selling my in-laws house. He was always responsive and gave guidance to make the selling process as simple as possible. Now my mom has him as her realtor to both buy and sell. If you're reading reviews then you might be on the fence or just want to make sure Cody lives up to all the hype. He does. Just let Cody take care of you.",
    initials: 'EM',
    date: 'Jan 2025',
  },
  {
    name: 'Brad & Amaya Donnelly',
    role: 'Home Buyer',
    quote: "Cody was absolutely phenomenal, dealing with an out of state title company. If your looking for a man that knows the law that has what seems to be an endless supply of knowledge, to an individual that will fight for you from the beginning to the end. Cody Posey is the agent everyone looks for but can never seem to find. I highly recommend working with Cody in any situation.",
    initials: 'BD',
    date: 'Nov 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'Marjorie Herbert',
    role: 'Home Buyer',
    quote: 'Cody Posey is an excellent realtor who puts his clients needs before anything else. He worked with me and my son and daughter-in-law to find a house that had a room to accommodate my baby grand piano. He spent numerous weekends patiently showing us multiple properties that would meet our needs. Finally he found the perfect home for me in a gated community for people over 55 years of age. He is warm, friendly and kind. I have recommended him to others and would go to him if seeking another property in New Braunfels or the surrounding areas.',
    initials: 'MH',
    date: 'Oct 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'Mike McCown',
    role: 'Home Inspector',
    quote: "I've had the pleasure of working with Cody as the home inspector for mutual clients navigating the home purchase process. In all of my interactions with him, he has consistently shown all of the qualities that make for an exceptional Realtor. High integrity, excellent communication skills, relentless work ethic, and a passion for taking care of his clients by prioritizing their needs, protecting their interests, and educating them throughout the transaction. I highly recommend Cody to anyone looking for a reliable and professional Realtor.",
    initials: 'MC',
    date: 'Sep 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'Gregory Beelek',
    role: 'Home Seller',
    quote: "Cody was always there to answer our questions and help guide us with the biggest change in our life and the sale of the first home we ever owned. When we needed to find services to get our home ready to sell, Cody had great recommendations that we found trustworthy and timely. It felt like he worked tirelessly and was a huge part of getting us under contract within 6 weeks of us listing our home. He was very respectful and cared so much that we recommended him to our daughter when she and her husband were ready to sell their home also. I hope anyone getting ready to sell their home is able to find a great partner like Cody was for us.",
    initials: 'GB',
    date: 'Aug 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'Ginger Browning',
    role: 'Fellow Agent',
    quote: 'I had the pleasure of working with Cody on the opposite side of a transaction. I represented the seller and he represented the buyer. He was professional and kind throughout the transaction. His ability to work toward a common goal that benefited everyone while truly fulfilling his duties to his client was very refreshing.',
    initials: 'GB',
    date: 'Aug 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'Rene Paez',
    role: 'Out-of-State Agent',
    quote: "Had a great experience using Cody as my agent. I'm an agent in another state but wanted to make sure I used someone local that knew the area well. Cody didn't disappoint and was able to educate me on all the differences in TX compared to other states. I highly recommend him.",
    initials: 'RP',
    date: 'Jul 2024',
  },
  {
    name: 'David Abrahams',
    role: 'Google Local Guide',
    quote: "Cody is conscientious, hard-working and passionate about finding the right property for his clients. He listens well, and works relentlessly until his client's needs have been fully met. There is no one better I would recommend for real estate assistance in New Braunfels and the surrounding area!",
    initials: 'DA',
    date: 'May 2024',
  },
];

const REVIEWS_PER_PAGE = 6;
const totalPages = Math.ceil(testimonials.length / REVIEWS_PER_PAGE);
---

<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  schema={pageSchema}
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="testi-hero">
      <div class="testi-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="testi-hero__content">
        <h1>Testimonials</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Reviews with Pagination -->
    <section class="testi-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="testi-list" id="testiList">
          {testimonials.map((t, i) => (
            <div class="testi-item" data-review-index={i} style={i >= REVIEWS_PER_PAGE ? 'display:none;' : ''}>
              <div class="testi-item__icon">
                <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#fff">
                  <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <blockquote class="testi-item__quote">&ldquo;{t.quote}&rdquo;</blockquote>
              <button class="testi-item__readmore" aria-expanded="false">READ MORE &#9662;</button>
              <div class="testi-item__name">&mdash; {t.name.toUpperCase()}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Pagination -->
        <div class="testi-pagination" id="testiPagination">
          {Array.from({ length: totalPages }, (_, i) => (
            <button
              class={`testi-pagination__btn ${i === 0 ? 'testi-pagination__btn--active' : ''}`}
              data-page={i}
            >
              {i + 1}
            </button>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Cody's Approach -->
    <section style="padding:4rem 0;background:#fff;">
      <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
        <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2rem;">Why Clients Trust <span class="accent">Cody Posey</span></h2>
        <p style="color:#555;line-height:1.8;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">The reviews on this page reflect a consistent theme: genuine care, clear communication, deep market knowledge, and a willingness to go above and beyond. These are not just values I talk about — they are the foundation of how I operate in every transaction, whether you are buying your first home, selling a property you have owned for decades, or navigating a complex relocation from across the country.</p>
        <p style="color:#555;line-height:1.8;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">My approach to real estate is rooted in 20 years of military service, where I learned that trust is earned through action, not words. Every client I work with receives the same level of attention and dedication, regardless of price point. I am responsive, transparent about market conditions, and honest about what to expect — even when the truth is not what people want to hear.</p>
        <p style="color:#555;line-height:1.8;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">I also believe in education. Buying or selling a home is one of the largest financial decisions most people will ever make, and I want my clients to understand every step of the process. That means explaining contracts in plain language, walking through inspection reports in detail, and making sure you understand the numbers before you sign anything. An informed client is a confident client.</p>
        <p style="color:#555;line-height:1.8;font-size:0.95rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">If you are considering working with me, I invite you to read these testimonials and then reach out for a conversation. No pressure, no sales pitch — just an honest discussion about your goals and how I can help you achieve them.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions About Working with Cody</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do I get started working with you?</summary>
            <p>The best way to start is with a phone call or text. I am available at (830) 360-5569 and happy to have an initial conversation about your goals, timeline, and questions. There is no obligation and no pressure. If we are a good fit, we will set up a plan and move forward at your pace. You can also fill out the contact form on this page.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Do you work with out-of-state buyers?</summary>
            <p>Absolutely. A significant portion of my business comes from buyers relocating from other states — particularly California, the Northeast, and other parts of Texas. I am experienced in remote home searches, video tours, and coordinating the purchase process for clients who cannot be physically present for every step. Several of the testimonials on this page are from out-of-state clients.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Are these real reviews from actual clients?</summary>
            <p>Yes. Every testimonial on this page comes from a verified client or professional I have worked with. Most of these reviews are publicly available on my Google Business Profile where you can read them directly. I am proud of the relationships I have built with my clients, and their feedback is the best measure of the service I provide.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="testi-cta">
      <div class="testi-cta__overlay"></div>
      <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
        <h2>Ready to Get <span class="accent">Started</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">Whether you're buying, selling, or just have questions about the New Braunfels market &mdash; I'm here to help.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Let's Connect</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ParallaxBanner image="/images/generated/home-interior-hc.png" />

  <ContactForm context="I'd like to work with Cody..." />
  <Footer />

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do I get started working with you?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The best way to start is with a phone call or text at (830) 360-5569. There is no obligation and no pressure. You can also fill out the contact form on the website."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you work with out-of-state buyers?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Absolutely. A significant portion of my business comes from buyers relocating from other states. I am experienced in remote home searches, video tours, and coordinating the purchase process for clients who cannot be present for every step."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Are these real reviews from actual clients?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. Every testimonial comes from a verified client or professional. Most are publicly available on my Google Business Profile."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .testi-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 350px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-image: url('/images/testimonials-hero.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    background-color: #333;
  }

  .testi-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .testi-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .testi-hero__content h1 {
    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  /* Testimonials Section */
  .testi-section {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .testi-list {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .testi-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .testi-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Red quote circle */
  .testi-item__icon {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #FF1616;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Quote text — collapsed by default, show first 200 chars */
  .testi-item__quote {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-style: normal;
    max-width: 650px;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-height: 5.4em;
    transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
  }

  .testi-item.expanded .testi-item__quote {
    max-height: 1000px;
  }

  /* Read More button */
  .testi-item__readmore {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #333;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .testi-item__readmore:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
    border-color: #FF1616;
  }

  .testi-item.expanded .testi-item__readmore {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Reviewer name */
  .testi-item__name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #333;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Pagination */
  .testi-pagination {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .testi-pagination__btn {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    color: #333;
  }

  .testi-pagination__btn:hover {
    border-color: #FF1616;
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .testi-pagination__btn--active {
    background: #FF1616;
    border-color: #FF1616;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .testi-pagination__btn--active:hover {
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* CTA Parallax */
  .testi-cta {
    position: relative;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    background-image: url('/images/testimonials-hero.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center bottom;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    background-color: #333;
  }

  .testi-cta__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  .testi-cta h2 {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .faq-section { padding: 4rem 0; background: #f9f9f9; }
  .faq-section h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .faq-list { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-item { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #eee; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .faq-item summary { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.3rem; color: #FF1616; font-weight: 700; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '\2212'; }
  .faq-item p { padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .testi-cta {
      background-attachment: scroll;
    }

    .testi-item__icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }

    .testi-item__icon svg {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
    }

    .testi-hero {
      height: 280px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script is:inline>
  const REVIEWS_PER_PAGE = 6;
  const items = document.querySelectorAll('.testi-item');
  const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.testi-pagination__btn');

  function showPage(pageIndex) {
    const start = pageIndex * REVIEWS_PER_PAGE;
    const end = start + REVIEWS_PER_PAGE;

    items.forEach((item, i) => {
      if (i >= start && i < end) {
        item.style.display = 'flex';
        item.classList.remove('expanded');
      } else {
        item.style.display = 'none';
      }
    });

    buttons.forEach(btn => {
      const active = parseInt(btn.dataset.page) === pageIndex;
      btn.classList.toggle('testi-pagination__btn--active', active);
    });

    document.querySelector('.testi-section')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
  }

  // Read More toggle
  document.querySelectorAll('.testi-item__readmore').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      btn.closest('.testi-item')?.classList.add('expanded');
    });
  });

  // Pagination
  buttons.forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      showPage(parseInt(btn.dataset.page));
    });
  });
</script>
